      "text": "ああ貴方は\n三枝さんの所の……お名前はなんだったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you’re from Saegusa-san’s…\nMy apologies‚ I forgot your name.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
